summary: This mod adds a small shack in the forest with all the things you need.
descriptionHtml:
This mod adds a small shack in the forest with all the things you need, which includes:

- AlchemyEnchanting stations
- Anvil, workbench and grinding stone
- Wood chopping block
- Tanning rack

The shack has a basement with three bookshelves, and comes with containers for almost every need.
To get there just get out of Shor\'s Stone facing South and take a turn to your right. Go deep into the forest and you will see the shack marker on your compass.

If you find any bugs or if you have any suggestions just let me know, I\'ll be updating if I come up with something new. 

Thanks for downloading!
author: SuN
